        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "The problem is the class Zend\\Db\\Adapter\\Adapter.\r\n\r\nWe have methods setQueryMode() and getQueryMode(), but query() method uses only the parameter 2 to determine the query mode. So, we have two solutions :\r\n* setQueryMode() is useless, and we delete them\r\n* change query() to use getQueryMode() if we use the default value of the parameter 2"
